The 2023 Great New York State Fair will take place August 23 through September 4, featuring all your fair-going favorites:
- Food and beverage including some of the Fair's most iconic culinary experiences, such as the Pizze Fritte, sausage sandwiches, and wine slushies;
- Daily concerts from national touring performers in the scenic, spacious New York Experience festival grounds;
- Thrilling amusement rides, games, and attractions for all ages on the Midway;
- Farm animals on display to introduce the young and young-at-heart to New York's agriculture;
- The I LOVE NY booth featuring an AR tour of New York, prizes, and more unique experiences!
Scheduled performers at the 2023 Great New York State Fair include REO Speedwagon, Tyler Hubbard, Theory of a Deadman, George Thorogood and The Destroyers, Chubby Checker, Bret Michaels, The Prodigals, Matt Stell, and more!

